OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy across northern areas with
OL,7,Foccasional rain or drizzle, mainly
OL,8,Facross northwest Scotland. Elsewhere,
OL,9,Fdry with clear spells. Perhaps some
OL,10,Fmist and fog patches developing
OL,11,Ftowards dawn, mainly in the west. A
OL,12,Fwarm night for most.
