OL,14,CWednesday:FStaying cloudy with patchy
OL,15,Frain in far northwestern Scotland. Dry
OL,16,Felsewhere with plenty of sunshine.
OL,17,FVery warm widely but feeling hot
OL,18,Facross southern and central England in
OL,19,Fthe strong sunshine.
